span><hr size=1> remember how you had to collect different things to get a piece of the vp key. Maybe each link needed for vex thal key is made up of mini quest. And this may be an item for one of the harder quest seeing as how it isnt real easy to get. I would think they would make the quest for a vex thal key long and invloved, since they love time sinks so much. I mean look how boring the vp key is, and luclin is way different than kunark, and vex thal will own ntov and vp, so the key quest will be long as hell.<br>
<br>
my 2 cents<br>
<br>
